  "description": "<ul><li>Manage the full end-to-end recruitment lifecycle, from talent sourcing and screening to interviewing and making hiring recommendations that drive successful placements.</li><li>Coordinate a smooth and engaging onboarding experience, including preparation and administration of employment contracts.</li><li>Collaborate closely with internal stakeholders and take on additional responsibilities that support team and business objectives.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested candidates, please email your resume to annasee@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p></p><p>Anna See Sing Yee</p><p>CEI Reg R25157535</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 99C4599</p><p></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p><p></p>",
